{"tid":1594913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】美參眾兩院外交委員會 分別通過《香港人權及民主法案》","createTime":"2019-09-25T20:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T20:36:59.000Z","uid":135077,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64349fa559e42d498351a711f519a879cffc6ed9","tid":1594913,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:00:42.000Z","msg":"香港爆發《逃犯條例》修訂爭議後，美國多名國會議員今年6月重新提出《香港人權及民主法案》，要求美國國務卿每年審視香港的自治情況，手段包括中止《美國&mdash;香港政策法》，取消香港特殊地位。美國參眾兩院外交委員會在美國時間周三，分別審議《香港人權及民主法案》。眾院外交事務委員的會議首先召開，並議決通過《法案》及《保護香港法》，眾議院的大會將會受理《法案》，踏出立法的重要一步。參院外交關係委員會在稍後的會議中，亦通過參院版《法案》。據知，參眾兩院委員會通過的版本並不完全相同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果》早前了解，眾議院外交事務委員會已就其版本達成共識，參議院的外交關係委員會則有就內容改動協商，但預期兩院委員會本周都可完成審議。眾議院外交事務委員會主席、民主黨眾議員恩格爾（Eliot Engel）回應查詢時表示，委員會討論後大會需時數周審議，暫沒有確實通過日期，並指即使法案會有修正案，也無礙審議進程。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨眾議員史密斯（Chris Smith）則表示，《法案》會以「開快車」（It is on a fast track for passage）方式排期審議，最多三至四周就可通過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190926/60084572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F60084572&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXThZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=edbfe889\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F60084572&h=519e3030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190926/60084572</a>"},{"pid":"e496206725fa2a9297fc7d35645b3757f4069bba","tid":1594913,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:04:47.000Z","msg":"SIR"},{"pid":"072808d03ea2d543f8610db046d02eeeac0dfc99","tid":1594913,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"welcome sir"},{"pid":"09a847f668bea9a11a05df43a8915f84acd358d6","tid":1594913,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:34:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26b5cd8c41780791007fd76a2da3238b930116b","tid":1594913,"uid":307180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9390381d47a7d125a13d56a559cdd6249e693f","tid":1594913,"uid":307180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:36:59.000Z","msg":"sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}